{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"443","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"暖化2°C內也難避免 研究：乾旱使部分作物分泌更多毒素","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>氣候變遷可能毒害全世界最貧困的人口，因為有些農作物因應氣溫上升的方式是增加有毒物質的分泌。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>根據英國獨立報報導，當乾旱來襲，玉米、豆類和木薯等植物會大量產生硝酸鹽（Nitrates）和氰化氫（hydrogen cyanide），這些物質對家畜和人類都是致命的。另一個問題是，溫暖的天氣促進有毒真菌傳染病的散佈，這些疾病已經導致非洲每年數以千計的肝癌病例。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>雖然這些問題在氣溫較高的發展中國家較嚴重，但科學家預測，若溫度繼續上升，可能會開始往北擴散。</p>\n\n<div class='align-center' style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>\n<figure class='image' style='text-align: inherit; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 1024px;'><a href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/eu_echo/25761999394/in/photolist-FfuYTm-FfFAVR-FKPYuE-G8DyEE-G8DPu9-FKQ9YL-FKQ6Gq-FfEWZF-Eb7n79-Edrqxr-Dg3wKv-Edrrhn-Eb7nud-Bwapwy-xknP1S-wpivBX-xiRiA9-wpfYGz-x4xak3-wphsx2-x4Cm62-x4x8fw-wp7gKw-x4Cn6D-x4xg9Q-xmGK7e-wp9JwJ-x4ChJx-x4F7vk-x3UiyT-tLDUra-sPwvEq-tJbV7E-ttWuGd-ttWuwy-tLcGgw-uvjWAp-tyiEbS-uvk5D8-tyiMcf-udK3Nd-uQ5ntM-uvkc42-udSHy4-LFYKNB-Knpbic-JQX1Yf-JQWYpY-JZ49ww-L4cH8K' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(95, 151, 8); text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'><img alt='衣索比亞乾旱。圖片來源：EU Civil Protection and Humanitarian Aid Operations(CC BY-NC-ND 2.0)' height='683' src='https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7809/46708451954_49b2d421b7_b.jpg' style='border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block;' width='1024' /></a>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<figcaption style='margin: 0px; padding: 10px 1em 0.6em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-align: left;'>衣索比亞乾旱。圖片來源：EU Civil Protection and Humanitarian Aid Operations（CC BY-NC-ND 2.0）</figcaption>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n<h3 style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.477; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>衣索比亞乾旱 農民、牲畜不明原因死亡</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>聯合國環境規劃署前首席科學家葛雷德（Jacqueline McGlade）教授在倫敦格雷沙姆學院（Gresham College）的講座上提出了警訊。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>衣索比亞傳出貧困的農民和他們的牲畜不明原因死亡，讓葛雷德注意到這個問題。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>衣國當時面臨乾旱，但這無法解釋為什麼某些病例出現神經問題，包括失明、行動不良和死亡。在當地工作的研究人員發現，乾旱破壞了農民的作物，迫使人們必須食用路邊的野生植物。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>不幸的是，乾旱的壓力也引發了這些植物內部的防禦機制，使其充滿了氰化氫。</p>\n\n<h3 style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.477; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>暖化衝擊食品安全&nbsp;聯合國、歐盟都示警</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>葛雷德和他的科學團隊於2016年收集了該現象的所有相關資料，彙整成一份報告提供給聯合國。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>後來，聯合國政府間氣候變遷專門委員會（IPCC）在最新的調查報告中，闡明全球暖化對全球極端天氣和糧食系統的影響。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>科學家認為這些影響已經使人有感，例如去年從加州到瑞典的極端熱浪，以及乾旱引發作物相關的恐慌，英國有農民稱某些蔬菜產量減少了一半。但是問題可能越來越嚴重。例如在乾旱條件下，玉米和其他作物上的真菌會產生黃麴毒素，而這種化學物質的擴散已超出其正常範圍。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>歐洲食品標準局警告，黃麴毒素與癌症、免疫問題和胎兒發育遲緩有關，很可能成為歐洲食品安全問題，即使全球溫度上升限制在2&deg;C內也難以避免。</p>\n\n<h3 style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.477; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>尋找高韌性作物 耐熱、耐病原生種受青睞</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>儘管如此，葛雷德認為未來有機會藉著耐熱、耐病的當地原生種和野生作物解決這個問題。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>生物多樣性國際組織研究員法達（Carlo Fadda）博士表示，他一直致力於研究衣索比亞種植了4000年的大麥和硬粒小麥品種。「這些品種很耐旱，即使欠年也保持相對良好的生產力，很少患病。」他說。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 19.2px;'>透過結合這些高韌性的作物與乾旱和疾病監測系統，葛雷德表示希望可以避免有毒作物的最嚴重影響。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><strong>資料來源：https://e-info.org.tw/node/217036</strong></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-04-11","clk_count":"18"}},"__N_SSG":true}